SUMMARY:Batik Scarf Coloring (sign up by 4/24)
DESCRIPTION:Santa Rosa Creative Circle\n**Brought to you by guest Batik ar
 tist Voonbin Pettit**\n\n**Join us for a 3-hour Batik Scarf Coloring Works
 hop! This workshop is open to all ages and is perfect for a fun\, creative
  experience.**\n\n**You’ll work on a 21'' x 21'' pre-waxed cotton scarf\
 , selecting from a variety of designs before the class. Plus\, you’ll ge
 t the chance to use a tjanting tool (wax pen) to add a personal touch by s
 igning your name on your piece.**\n\n**We’ll introduce you to various ba
 tik coloring techniques\, showing you how to blend colors and create uniqu
 e effects on fabric.**\n\n**We’ll also take care of the wax removal proc
 ess. Your completed scarf will be mailed to you\, ready to wear or display
  as a unique piece of art.**\n\n**Schedule:**\n**• 12:30–1:00 PM – I
 ntroduction to batik and coloring techniques**\n**• 1:00–3:30 PM – B
 atik coloring session**\n\n**Sign up here:**\n**https://www.iridescentbati
 k.com/workshops/69**\n\n**Note: Once you’ve signed up\, the instructor w
 ill email you a selection of scarf templates to choose from for the worksh
 op.**\n\n**Please note that we do not accept last-minute design changes th
 e night before the workshop.**
